    "body": "I _think_ Monster Tank Madness could be fixed by having an at-first unused player and then changing the owner of the mad tanks instead of using `SetStance`. Then `Player.SetStance` could be removed as well.\n\nCould you make the lobby check box placement between TD and the other mods consistent, please? In TD, Build Off Allied ConYards, Short Game and Crates are switched compared the other mods (I think I'd prefer TD's layout: 1st column visibility, 2nd column balancing, 3rd column misc.). My muscle memory will thank you :)\n"
