    "body": "While I can understand that this feature needs to be removed (since, according to you, it's buggy), I still think this Diplomacy option could be useful in third-party mods like this one: http://www.sleipnirstuff.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=83&p=290395\n\nExample: Player A (who manages policemen) wants to switch teams with Player B (who plays Firefighters), while Player C wants an AI bot to take over his Ambulance faction. What I mean is that this option makes sense for some mods (but maybe not for our 3/4 main mods, I can agree with that).\n"
